          "name": "Battlecry!",
          "page": 186,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "If a large city's waste management system spirals out of control, ofalths can grow and propagate unchecked. These reeking creatures haul tons of trash on their backs and carry a particularly virulent disease.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
