            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The ofalth stampede hurls a tremendous amount of rotting trash, which rains down in a 10-foot burst within 60 feet. All creatures in the area take 4d10 bludgeoning damage (DC 33 basic Reflex save). Creatures that fail the saving throw are also exposed to wretched weeps. When the troop is reduced to 2 segments, the area decreases to a 5-foot burst.",
